rows.label: tlk45320122_06_msg0001
rows.name:
Gah... If only there was someone
who could help...

rows.label: tlk45320122_06_msg0002
rows.name: This is just between you and me...

rows.label: tlk45320122_06_msg0003
rows.name:
We've received information that the
rebel group is doing business in
Gula.

rows.label: tlk45320122_06_msg0004
rows.name:
We want to catch the ringleaders and
put a stop to their business activities.

rows.label: tlk45320122_06_msg0005
rows.name:
If we, the Superbian army, were
sent there, they might just stop
their business and vanish.

rows.label: tlk45320122_06_msg0006
rows.name:
To avoid that we're trying to recruit
capable folk with no connection to us
to take on this mission.

rows.label: tlk45320122_06_msg0007
rows.name:
But no worthy candidates have
appeared, yet...

rows.label: tlk45320122_06_msg0009
rows.name:
Now that I know you're on the mission
I'm feeling hopeful.

rows.label: tlk45320122_06_msg0010
rows.name: I heard that some of them are armed.

rows.label: tlk45320122_06_msg0011
rows.name:
You'd better make good your
preparations, and take care out there.
